title: Come Elevate your lifestyle here at The Retreat at Bothell!
posting_body: ['Welcome Home', 'Welcome to our incredible family and pet friendly luxury apartment community located in Bothell, WA, featuring 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartment homes.', 'Just 20 miles northeast of Seattle, near I-405 and Route 522, this apartment community makes a great home for both workers in the Seattle area, and Bothell itself – a lively member of the biotechnology and software industries.', 'Right next door to Amazon/Microsoft private bus line as well as on site bus route for k-12 students.', 'Whether you’re interested in a 2 bedroom Bothell apartment, or a 1 or 3 bedroom
